Largely based on https://github.com/VictoriaMetrics/VictoriaMetrics

Start: docker-compose up
Stop (and lose some data): docker-compose down

Clean up (WITH DATA!!!): git clean -fd

To configure external hosts, check for external-example/collectd.conf
!!!! Attention on --no-install-recommends, otherwise in ubuntu it might install full desktop.
apt install --no-install-recommends collectd
